Quarter: The fiscal quarter for which the facility costs are reported, e.g., 'Q3 2025'.
Facility_Costs: Total facility costs incurred during the specified quarter. This includes expenses related to physical infrastructure, utilities, and maintenance.
Annual_Revenue_Category: The annual revenue range of the company during the reporting period, providing context to the cost data.
Compliance_Certifications: List of compliance certifications held by the company, indicating adherence to regulatory standards during the reporting period.
Headquarters_Location: The location of the company's headquarters, providing geographic context relevant to the facility costs.
